<table width="auto"  border="0" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0"><tr><td colspan=3>House Bill/Resolution NO. <b>HB00090</b></td></tr><tr><td colspan=3>FULL TITLE : AN ACT PROVIDING FOR THE MODERNIZATION OF THE PHILIPPINE TRANSPORTATION INFRASTRUCTURE, APPROPRIATING FUNDS THEREFOR, AND FOR OTHER PURPOSES</td></tr><tr><td colspan=3>ABSTRACT : Mandates the Department of Transportation in consultation with the NEDA, DPWH, DBM, and other sectoral agencies to submit the Transportation Infrastructure Modernization Program containing specific plans for the aviation, railway, maritime and land transportation sectors to the Congressional Oversight Committee for the purpose of developing an efficient and reliable transportation system. </td></tr><tr><td colspan=3>ALIAS NAME : “Philippine Transportation Infrastructure Modernization Act.”</td></tr><tr><td colspan=3>PRINCIPAL AUTHOR/S : <b>SARMIENTO, EDGAR S.</b></td></tr><tr><td colspan=3>DATE FILED : 2019-07-01</td></tr><tr><td colspan=3>SIGNIFICANCE: NATIONAL</td></tr><tr><td colspan=3>CO-AUTHORS (Journal Entries) :</td></tr><tr><td>1. Eriguel (000 2019-11-18)</td><tr><td colspan=3><b>ACTIONS TAKEN BY THE COMMITTEE ON RULES</b></td></tr><tr><td colspan=3>REFERRAL TO THE COMMITTEE ON TRANSPORTATION ON 2019-07-23</td></tr></table>